'''''The Devil Inside''''' is an American [[supernatural]] [[horror film]] directed and co-written by [[William Brent Bell]], as a documentary-style film about a woman who becomes involved in a series of [[exorcism in Christianity|exorcism]]s during her quest to determine what happened to her mother, a woman who murdered three people as a result of being [[Demonic possession|possessed by a demon]]. Produced by Morris Paulson and [[Matthew Peterman]],<ref name="HR"/>, the film stars Fernanda Andrade, [[Simon Quarterman]], Evan Helmuth and Suzan Crowley, and is slated to be released theatrically on February 24, 2012.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.webcitation.org/63Z8skA7a | title=<U+201C>THE DEVIL INSIDE<U+201D> gets a release date | publisher=[[Fangoria]] | date=April 20, 2011 | accessdate=November 29, 2011 | author=Dart, Allan}}</ref><ref name="DC">{{cite web | url=http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/43873/paramount-insurge-reveal-devil-inside | title=Paramount Insurge to Reveal The Devil Inside | publisher=[[Dread Central]] | date=April 16, 2011 | accessdate=November 29, 2011 | author=Uncle Creepy}}</ref>

==Background==
Director Bell, and Morris Paulson and [[Matthew Peterman]] shot the film in 2010 in locations in [[Rome]] and [[Bucharest]]. [[Lorenzo di Bonaventura]] and Steven Schneider brought the movie to [[Paramount Pictures]],<ref name="HR"/><ref name="V">{{cite news | url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118035756 | title=Big players eye more low-budget fare | work=[[Variety]] | date=April 23, 2011 | accessdate=November 29, 2011 | author=Goldstein, Gregg}}</ref> and their low-budget branch, [[Paramount Pictures#Insurge Pictures|Paramount Insurge]] acquired the film, hoping it would be its next ''[[Paranormal Activity (film)|Paranormal Activity]]''.<ref name="HR">{{cite news | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/blogs/heat-vision/paramount-bets-devil-paranormal-activity-96393 | title=Paramount Bets 'The Devil Inside' Is Its Next 'Paranormal Activity' | work=[[Hollywood Reporter]] | date=February 3, 2011 | accessdate=November 29, 2011 | author=Kit, Borys}}</ref> 

